'''提摩西·麥斯威爾·「馬克斯」·凱澤'''（{{lang-en|Timothy Maxwell "Max" Keiser}}，{{bd|1960年|1月23日||}}）是[[美國|美國]]電視和廣播節目主持人，現與其妻{{link-de|史黛西·赫伯特|Stacy Herbert}}共同主持《{{le|凱澤報告|Keiser Report}}》，於[[RT電視台|RT電視台]]播出。

== 生平 ==

凱澤在[[紐約州|紐約州]]的[[西徹斯特郡|西徹斯特郡]]出生和成長。就讀於[[紐約大學|紐約大學]]。早年曾從事過許多工作，包括在[[華爾街|華爾街]]成為一名[[證券經紀人|證券經紀人]]<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Max Keiser: 'Barack Obama is clueless. Mitt Romney will bankrupt the|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/max-keiser-barack-obama-clueless-mitt-romney-will-bankrupt-country-8269633.html|accessdate=2021-02-02|date=2012-11-05|work=The Independent|language=en|archive-date=2021-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210516080820/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/max-keiser-barack-obama-clueless-mitt-romney-will-bankrupt-country-8269633.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2004年，凱澤與《生態學家》總編輯[[扎克·戈德史密斯|扎克·戈德史密斯]]合作，成立了一家名叫Karmabanque的[[對沖基金|對沖基金]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Campaign aims to hit Coke where it hurts|url=https://www.theguardian.com/business/2004/nov/25/2|accessdate=2021-02-02|date=2004-11-25|last=Marinko|first=Paul|publisher=the Guardian|language=en|archive-date=2021-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210504115347/http://www.theguardian.com/business/2004/nov/25/2|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Hedge Funds Banking on Social and Moral Issues|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/articles/A25215-2004Dec24.html|accessdate=2021-02-02|date=2004-12-25|publisher=Washington Post|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211070117/https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/articles/A25215-2004Dec24.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Notebook: Iconic dotcom has lost its way|url=https://www.theguardian.com/business/2004/nov/26/9|accessdate=2021-02-02|date=2004-11-26|publisher=the Guardian|language=en|archive-date=2017-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171223102355/https://www.theguardian.com/business/2004/nov/26/9|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

自2009年9月起，凱澤與妻子史黛西·赫伯特共同主持財經評論節目《凱澤報告》，於RT電視台播出<ref name=":0" />。《凱澤報告》在2011年9月播出的一集中採訪了喜劇女演員[[羅珊·巴爾|羅珊·巴爾]]，巴爾在節目中諷刺性地說她對金融危機的解決方案是「把[[斷頭台|斷頭台]]帶回來」<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=Roseanne Barr: 'Guilty' Wall Street Bankers Should Be Sent to Reeducation Camps or Beheaded|url=https://www.foxnews.com/entertainment/roseanne-barr-guilty-wall-street-bankers-should-be-sent-to-reeducation-camps-or-beheaded|accessdate=2021-02-02|date=2015-03-26|work=Fox News|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210302175645/https://www.foxnews.com/entertainment/roseanne-barr-guilty-wall-street-bankers-should-be-sent-to-reeducation-camps-or-beheaded|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

